\c 36
\s Vana vaEsau
\p
\v 1 Ndiwoka marudzi aEsau unova Edhomu:
\v 2 Esau wakatora vakadzi vake kuvakunda veKanani, Adha, mukunda waEroni muHeti, naHoribhama mukunda waAna, mukunda waZibhioni muHivhi,
\v 3 naBhasimati mukunda waIshimaeri hanzvadzi yaNebhayoti.
\v 4 Adha ndokubereka Esau Erifazi; Bhasimati ndokubereka Rueri;
\v 5 Ohori­bhama ndokubereka Jeushi naJarami naKora; ava vanakomana vaEsau, vaakaberekerwa panyika yeKanani.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Esau wakatora vakadzi vake nevanakomana vake nevakunda vake, nemweya yose yeimba yake, nemombe dzake nezvipfuwo zvake zvose, nenhumbi dzake dzose dzaakange awana munyika yeKanani, ndokuenda kune \add imwe \add*nyika achibva pachiso chaJakobho munun'una wake.
\v 7 Nekuti zvipfuwo zvavo zvakange zvakawanda zvokuti vaiva vasingagoni kugara pamwe, uye nyika yeutorwa hwavo yakange isingagoni kuvatakura nekuda kwezvipfuwo zvavo.
\v 8 Esau ndokugara kugomo reSeiri; Esau ndiye Edhomu.
\p
\v 9 Zvino awa marudzi aEsau, baba vevaEdhomu, kugomo reSeiri;
\v 10 awa mazita evanakomana vaEsau, Erifazi mwana­komana waAdha mukadzi waEsau, Rueri mwanakomana waBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\v 11 Nevanakomana vaEri­fazi vaiva Temani, Omari, Zefo, naGatamu, naKenazi.
\v 12 Zvino Timuna waiva murongo waErifazi, mwanakomana waEsau; wakaberekera Erifazi muAma­reki; ava vanakomana vaAdha muka­dzi waEsau.
\v 13 Zvino ava vanakomana vaRueri, Nahati naZera, Shama naMiza; ava vanakomana vaBhasimati mukadzi waEsau.
\p
\v 14 Zvino ava vanakomana vaOhoribhama mu­kunda waAna, mukunda waZibhioni mukadzi waEsau, ndokumuberekera Esau Jeushi, naJarami, naKora.
\p
\v 15 Ava ndivo madzishe pakati pavana vaEsau: Vanakomana vaErifazi, dangwe raEsau: Ishe Temani, nashe Omari, nashe Zefo, nashe Kenazi,
\v 16 nashe Kora, nashe Gatamu, nashe Amareki; ndiwo madzishe okwaErifazi munyika yeEdhomu; ndivo vanakomana vaAdha.
\p
\v 17 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaRueri, mwanakomana waEsau: Ishe Nahati, na­she Zera, nashe Shama, nashe Miza; ndiwo madzishe okwaRueri munyika yeEdhomu; ndivo vanakomana vaBhasi­mati, mukadzi waEsau.
\p
\v 18 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaOhori­bhama, mukadzi waEsau: Ishe Jeushi, nashe Jarami, nashe Kora; ndiwo madzi­she okwaOhoribhama, mukunda waAna, mukadzi waEsau.
\v 19 Ndivo vanakomana vaEsau, ndiwo madzishe avo; ndiye Edhomu.
\p
\v 20 Ndivo vanakomana vaSeiri, muHori, vaigara panyika iyo: Rotani, naSho­bharu, naZibhioni, naAna,
\v 21 naDhishoni, naEzeri, naDhishani; ndiwo madzishe okuvaHori, vanakomana vaSeiri munyika yeEdhomu.
\p
\v 22 Vanakomana vaRotani, vaiva Hori, naHemani; hanzvadzi yaRotani aiva Timuna.
\p
\v 23 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaSho­bharu: Avhani, naManahati, naEbhari, naShefo, naOnamu.
\p
\v 24 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaZi­bhioni: Aja, naAna; ndiye Ana akawana matsime emvura inopisa kusango, achifu­dza mbongoro dzaZibhioni, baba vake.
\p
\v 25 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaAna: Dhi­shoni, naOhoribhama, mukunda waAna.
\p
\v 26 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaDhishoni: Hemudhani, naEshibhani, naIturani, naKerani.
\v 27 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaEzeri: Bhirihani, naZaavhani, naAkani.
\v 28 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaDhishani: Uzi naArani.
\p
\v 29 Ava ndiwo madzishe okuvaHori: Ishe Rotani, nashe Shobharu, nashe Zi­bhioni, nashe Ana,
\v 30 nashe Dhishoni, nashe Ezeri, nashe Dhishani; ndiwo ma­dzishe okuvaHori, namarudzi avo mu­nyika yeSeiri.
\p
\v 31 Ava ndivo madzimambo akabata ushe munyika yeEdhomu, vana vaIsiraeri vachigere kuva namadzimambo:
\v 32 Bhera, mwanakomana waBheori, akabata ushe paEdhomu; zita reguta rake rainzi Dhinihabha.
\v 33 Akafa, Jobhabhu, mwanakomana waZera weBhozara akabata ushe pachigaro chake.
\v 34 Jobhabhu akafa, Hushamu wenyika yavaTemani akabata ushe pachigaro chake.
\v 35 Hushamu akafa, Hadhadhi, mwanakomana waBhedhadhi, uya akauraya Midhiani kusango reMoabhu, akabata ushe pachigaro chake; zita reguta rake rainzi Avhiti.
\v 36 Hadhadhi akafa, Samura weMasereka akabata ushe pachigaro chake.
\v 37 Samura akafa, Shauri weRehobhoti paRwizi akabata ushe pachigaro chake.
\v 38 Shauri akafa, Bhaarihanani, mwanakomana waAkibhori akabata ushe pachigaro chake.
\v 39 Bhaarihanani, mwanakomana waAkibhori, akafa, Hadhari akabata ushe pachigaro chake; zita reguta rake rainzi Pau; zita romukadzi wake rainzi Mehetabheri, mukunda waMatiredhi, mukunda waMehazahadhi.
\p
\v 40 Aya ndiwo mazita amadzishe okwaEsau, nedzimba dzavo, namaguta avo, namazita avo; Ishe Timuna, nashe Arivha, nashe Jeteti;
\v 41 nashe Ohori­bhama, nashe Era, nashe Pinoni;
\v 42 na­she Kenazi, nashe Temani, nashe Mi­bhizari;
\v 43 nashe Magidhieri, nashe Iramu; ndiwo madzishe aEdhomu, maererano nenzvimbo dzavo dzokugara munyika yenhaka yavo. Ndiye Esau, baba vaEdhomu.
